OL,3,C'It will happen again': Concerns over
OL,4,Cfuture of Hoads Wood without new
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FThe clean-up of thousands of tonnes of
OL,8,Fillegally dumped waste in an ancient
OL,9,Fwoodland, in Kent, has been praised by
OL,10,Fcampaigners as concerns remain that
OL,11,Fwithout new measures "it will happen
OL,12,Fagain".
OL,14,FPictures show the operation to remove
OL,15,F30,000 tonnes of household and
OL,16,Fconstruction waste at Hoad's Wood, in
OL,17,FAshford, has made progress since it
OL,18,Fstarted a year ago.
OL,26,@sD@VOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
