CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781359875
OL,3,C'It will happen again': Concerns over
OL,4,Cfuture of Hoads Wood without new
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FThe Environment Agency began a
OL,8,Fcriminal investigation in 2023 after
OL,9,Fthe dumped waste was piled 15 feet
OL,10,Fhigh in places.
OL,12,FThree men were arrested in February
OL,13,Flast year and the public body said
OL,14,Fthey "remain very much part of
OL,15,Finquiries".
OL,26,@vD@FOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
