PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781359875
OL,3,C'It will happen again': Concerns over
OL,4,Cfuture of Hoads Wood without new
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FThe beauty spot is designated a site
OL,8,Fof special scientific interest, but
OL,9,Fwas described by local people as an
OL,10,F"environmental disaster" during
OL,11,Fcampaigning for the waste to be
OL,12,Fcleared.
OL,14,FPrevious pictures of the site show the
OL,15,Fscale of the rubbish mounting up and
OL,16,Fencroaching on a patch of bluebells,
OL,17,Fwhile blue water also swamped the area.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781359875
OL,3,C'It will happen again': Concerns over
OL,4,Cfuture of Hoads Wood without new
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FThe Environment Agency announced the
OL,8,Fclean-up operation, which began last
OL,9,FJune, is expected to cost up to #15
OL,10,Fmillion.
OL,12,FWaste crime costs England's economy
OL,13,Faround #1 billion a year.
OL,15,FA Rescue Hoad's Wood spokesperson said
OL,16,Fthe campaign group were "pleased" with
OL,17,Fthe removal action and contractor
OL,18,FAcumen has done a "very good job"
OL,19,Freducing the impact on the local area.
OL,26,@xD@YOUxD@aO]zD@SOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781359875
OL,3,C'It will happen again': Concerns over
OL,4,Cfuture of Hoads Wood without new
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FBut they added if long-term controls
OL,8,Fare not put in place the area will
OL,9,Fbecome "catnip" to fly-tippers and it
OL,10,Fwill "absolutely happen again".
OL,12,FThe group is calling for the private
OL,13,Fland sites to be transferred to a
OL,14,Fpublic authority to own and be
OL,15,Fresponsible for, including CCTV and
OL,16,Fcontrolled vehicle access to stop
OL,17,Ffurther dumping.
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@OO]rD@FOUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
