FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781359875
OL,3,C'It will happen again': Concerns over
OL,4,Cfuture of Hoads Wood without new
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FAn Environment Agency spokesman said:
OL,8,F"We share the public's anger on waste
OL,9,Fcrime. Our countryside and coastal
OL,10,Fareas spoiled by people who don't care
OL,11,Fabout the environment. It's just about
OL,12,Fmaking money.
OL,14,F"We will seek to claim any money back
OL,15,Ffrom the offenders."
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
