OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781359875
OL,3,C'It will happen again': Concerns over
OL,4,Cfuture of Hoads Wood without new
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FOn Hoad's Wood, the spokesman added:
OL,8,F"We are working with Natural England,
OL,9,FForestry Commission, Kent County
OL,10,FCouncil and Ashford Borough Council on
OL,11,Fplans for the site once clearance is
OL,12,Fcompleted, including options (that)
OL,13,Fare available to all organisations and
OL,14,Flandowners to facilitate the
OL,15,Fregeneration of the wood."
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@ZO]
